screen_desc: The screenshot displays a mobile app interface for managing payment methods. At the top, it shows the title "Payment" with a section for "Saved Payment Method," listing Google Pay. Below, there are options to "Add Payment Method," including Credit/Debit Card, PayPal, and Afterpay. Further down, it mentions "DoorDash Credits," indicating that the user's AUD credit will be applied to their next order, with a balance of A$0.00 AUD, applicable only in Australia. There are also options to redeem a gift card and invite friends to earn credits. The interface features a clean design with clear headings and options.
